let sortOrder = [true, true, true]; // Tracks sort order for each column

function populateTable() {
const tbody = document.querySelector('#facultyTable tbody');
tbody.innerHTML = ''; // Clear existing rows
facultyData.forEach(row => {
const tr = document.createElement('tr');
tr.innerHTML = `<td>${row.Name}</td><td>${row['Primary Position']}</td><td>${row['Total Base Pay']}</td>`;
tbody.appendChild(tr);
});
}

function searchTable() {
const nameInput = document.getElementById('nameSearchInput').value.toLowerCase();
const positionInput = document.getElementById('positionSearchInput').value.toLowerCase();
const nameRegex = new RegExp(nameInput, 'i');
const positionRegex = new RegExp(positionInput, 'i');
const rows = document.querySelectorAll('#facultyTable tbody tr');
rows.forEach(row => {
const name = row.querySelector('td:nth-child(1)').textContent.toLowerCase();
const position = row.querySelector('td:nth-child(2)').textContent.toLowerCase();
if (nameRegex.test(name) && positionRegex.test(position)) {
row.style.display = '';
} else {
row.style.display = 'none';
}
});
}

function sortTable(columnIndex) {
const tbody = document.querySelector('#facultyTable tbody');
const rowsArray = Array.from(tbody.querySelectorAll('tr'));
const isNumeric = columnIndex === 2;

rowsArray.sort((a, b) => {
const aText = a.querySelector(`td:nth-child(${columnIndex + 1})`).textContent;
const bText = b.querySelector(`td:nth-child(${columnIndex + 1})`).textContent;
const aValue = isNumeric ? parseFloat(aText.replace(/[$,]/g, '')) : aText.toLowerCase();
const bValue = isNumeric ? parseFloat(bText.replace(/[$,]/g, '')) : bText.toLowerCase();

if (aValue < bValue) {
return sortOrder[columnIndex] ? -1 : 1;
} else if (aValue > bValue) {
return sortOrder[columnIndex] ? 1 : -1;
} else {
return 0;
}
});

sortOrder[columnIndex] = !sortOrder[columnIndex]; // Toggle sort order

tbody.innerHTML = ''; // Clear existing rows
rowsArray.forEach(row => tbody.appendChild(row));
}

window.onload = populateTable;
</script>

</body>
</html>
